quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  8,34,"Nabo bali nende lilayi shina lia Nyasaye alabahelesia eshinyasio tawe, nikali mbu bekalilanga Abandu omusikiti kwa oluyali oko, ne shini abaliindi bakwo tawe? Toto abalindi bakwo ni balia abaria Nyasaye, ne abanji mubo shibamanyile shiosishiosi tawe."
  8,35,"Ne amalamo (iswala) kabu munzu yoluyali shikali shiosishiosi tawe halali okhupa emilosi nende amakhofi butswa. Kho pile eshinyasio shingala mwakhayanga aka Nyasaye."
  8,36,"Toto balia abakhaya barusinjia omwandu kwabu okhwikalila injila ya Nyasaye. Kho betsa okhukurusia mana kalababeela ameyitsulisio mana balashilwa. Ne balia abakhaya aka Nyasaye, balikhung’asibwa mumulilo."
  8,37,"Kho Nyasaye anyoole okhwawukhasia ababii nende abalayi, ne are abamabii hekulu ewa abamabii bandi, ne ababumbe boosi halala mana abasukune mumulilo. Abo nibo basikha muno."
  8,38,"Boolela balia bakhaya mbu: 'Nibalekha, balaleshelwa akabura. Ne nibakalushila, toto yamala okhubura imelo ya (Nyasaye yayakholela) abandu ba khale.'"
  8,39,"Ne khupane ninabo okhuula mumale amatemo nende okhusandibwa, ne idini ibe yosi shichila Nyasaye. Ne nibalekha, awo toto Nyasaye alolanga muno akabakholanga."
  8,40,"Ne ni bakalukhana, manye mbu Nyasaye niye Omwami wenyu, ni Omulesi nende Omukhoonyi omulayi muno."